not that tongue—in—cheek thing we usually do.

42:37.806 --> 42:40.297
I'm most serious
when my tongue's in my cheek.

42:40.434 --> 42:43.141
How serious an acknowledgement
are we talking about here?

42:43.270 --> 42:46.808
Well, like a riderless horse
at the head of the parade.

42:46.940 --> 42:50.808
The sacred purpose of Krewe du Vieux
is to mock the serious.

42:50.944 --> 42:54.562
- Vote.
— All in favor of a serious acknowledgement

42:54.698 --> 42:57.189
at the head of this year's
Krewe du Vieux parade?

42:57.325 --> 42:58.906
- No.
— Yes.

42:59.035 --> 43:00.445
— No.
— No.

43:00.579 --> 43:02.444
No.

43:08.128 --> 43:11.461
