43:16.636 --> 43:17.625
(Woman) Yes!

43:26.730 --> 43:28.015
Jesus.

43:28.148 --> 43:30.605
Hey!

43:32.819 --> 43:35.151
(Laughing)

43:37.407 --> 43:38.908
Wow!

43:42.287 --> 43:43.823
Oh!

43:45.165 --> 43:48.373
— How's it going?
— It's beautiful, no problems.

43:48.502 --> 43:50.538
The cops are a little freaked out
by the numbers,

43:50.670 --> 43:53.127
but I'm glad we got as many people
as we do volunteering.

43:53.256 --> 43:55.998
— Nobody expected this many people back.
— No.

43:57.344 --> 43:59.175
(Creighton laughing)

43:59.304 --> 44:01.545
This almost didn't happen.

44:01.681 --> 44:04.923
— This had to happen. It's great.
— Yeah.

44:05.060 --> 44:08.848
I'm gonna fall back and see
what's going on with the third division.

44:13.860 --> 44:15.361
(J‘ Drums beating)

44:24.746 --> 44:27.533
