45:01.032 --> 45:03.444
Oh, come on, VlPs! Go to work!

45:03.577 --> 45:05.693
Work, work, work!

45:05.829 --> 45:08.866
Work, VlPs! Work, work!

45:08.999 --> 45:10.614
(All chanting)

45:18.258 --> 45:21.045
- Kim!
— Whaah!

45:32.439 --> 45:34.805
Oh, my God, you made it!

45:58.381 --> 46:00.963
I'll be... I'll catch up with you.

46:01.092 --> 46:03.299
Go ahead, l'll catch up with you.

46:13.313 --> 46:15.053
Marcus, right?

46:16.316 --> 46:18.728
— Been wondering about my brother.
- How he doin'?

46:18.860 --> 46:21.602
