You seen him?

46:21.738 --> 46:25.071
Me?
l was in Atlanta till, like, New Year's.

46:26.368 --> 46:29.952
ljust need to know, before the storm,
was Daymo back to using?

46:30.080 --> 46:32.366
Wasn't copping from me if he was.

46:32.499 --> 46:34.490
Last I knew, he let the shit be.

46:36.503 --> 46:38.539
That's it?

46:38.672 --> 46:40.754
I'm just trying to figure it out, you know?

46:40.882 --> 46:43.168
If I hear something,
you got the bar open, right?

46:43.301 --> 46:45.758
Yeah. Yeah, I been back a while now.

46:45.887 --> 46:49.254
Figured it was time for me to come back too, see what's
happening.

46:49.391 --> 46:50.756
Yeah.

46:51.518 --> 46:53.474
OK, then.

46:53.603 --> 46:55.218
Take it easy.

46:59.526 --> 47:01.858
— (Man barking)
— (Whistles blowing)

47:22.799 --> 47:24.505
Davis!

47:26.886 --> 47:28.877
Janette! Hey, babe.

47:29.014 --> 47:31.756
You won't believe what happened to me
at the restaurant last night.

47:31.891 --> 47:34.348
You will not believe this!

47:34.477 --> 47:35.933
— Check it out!
- What?

47:36.062 --> 47:38.053
Check it out!

47:48.283 --> 47:51.195
— (Woman) Yeah, I'm gonna follow him!
— That was different.

47:51.327 --> 47:53.943
Oh, man, don't even try to act
like it wasn't fucking awesome.

47:54.080 --> 47:56.321
The band was fucking on fire, man.

47:56.458 --> 47:58.699
- (Gunfire)
— (Woman screaming)

48:15.935 --> 48:17.926
(Woman) He's shooting!

48:21.316 --> 48:23.022
Annie?

48:24.527 --> 48:26.188
Annie?

48:26.321 --> 48:28.983
(Man) We got a man down!
Man down, man down!

48:29.115 --> 48:31.492
— Man down.
- Annie!

48:34.204 --> 48:36.320
For many it was a stark reminder
of a New Orleans

48:36.456 --> 48:38.242
