48:38.374 --> 48:39.989
When the fuck did that happen?

48:40.126 --> 48:43.710
I didn't hear any gunshots.
l was at the whole second line, man.

48:46.758 --> 48:49.625
Three people shot.
You believe that shit?

48:49.761 --> 48:52.878
That's messed up.
That was a hell of a parade.

48:53.014 --> 48:55.972
