48:59.104 --> 49:03.564
"New Orleans niggers
will fuck up a wet dream."

49:03.691 --> 49:06.819
You know, now the media
is gonna freak the fuck out.

49:06.945 --> 49:09.652
- The cops... Shit.
— (Man) Hey, white boy.

49:09.781 --> 49:13.945
