49:38.476 --> 49:42.219
- Davis, shut up, man.
— He just dared me to say "nigger."

49:42.355 --> 49:45.847
— What is that all about? Like I'm like...
— Sh. Sh.

49:45.984 --> 49:48.020
"Sh? Sh?" All right.

49:48.153 --> 49:50.860
All right, all right. OK.

49:54.784 --> 49:58.902
Just for the sake of discussion,
what's gonna happen if I...

49:59.038 --> 50:01.165
(Man) Oh, man!

50:01.875 --> 50:03.911
Come on, man.

50:07.213 --> 50:10.455
— Davis, you OK, man?
- Fuck off! Fuck!

50:12.969 --> 50:15.085
Fuck this!

50:17.223 --> 50:21.136
— Wait up, Davis.
— Leave me the fuck alone, man!

50:27.233 --> 50:28.894
(Distant car alarm)

50:39.037 --> 50:40.868
(Annie crying)

50:40.997 --> 50:43.033
(Sonny) Sh.

50:52.675 --> 50:54.415
(Classical music playing)

50:59.724 --> 51:02.090
Donald, he's conscious.

51:07.774 --> 51:09.639
How the fuck...

