54:15.211 --> 54:17.418
You know, gathers his stuff up,

54:17.547 --> 54:20.084
calls for a guard, tells him that his time's up.

54:20.216 --> 54:22.673
It's time to let him go. Yeah.

54:22.802 --> 54:27.011
And the kid explains,
in New Orleans when you shoot someone,

54:27.140 --> 54:32.385
they hold you for 60 days and let you go,
which, let's face it, is pretty much what we do,

54:32.520 --> 54:35.227
given how fucked up
Eddie Jordan has the DA's office.

54:35.356 --> 54:38.894
Eddie's a joke, but his shop's
not the only one with problems.

54:39.026 --> 54:43.190
lam telling you, Toni,
the wheels are off the cart.

54:43.322 --> 54:46.189
