54:48.995 --> 54:50.986
And we ain't ready.

54:54.167 --> 54:56.453
But you want to talk about a trombone.

55:58.356 --> 56:00.267
Hey, you.

56:00.399 --> 56:02.776
Oh, you're reading your old stuff, huh?

56:02.902 --> 56:04.767
Thoreau had it wrong.

56:04.904 --> 56:07.896
